    </tr>
    </tbody>
</table> 


  <div style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 14px;">
   <p> <i>For cancellation and refund (if any), write an email to “<b>refund@reva.edu.in</b>”. Refund rules are governed by the UGC Notifications of October 2018.</i></p>
    </div>


   <div style="font-family: sans-serif;text-align: center;font-size: 14px;">
    <b>Undertaking and Declaration by the Student/Candidate and the Parent/Guardian</b>   
                </div>


   <div style="font-family: sans-serif;font-size: 14px;margin-top:8px;align:justify;">
      
          
        <i>The Remaining due/payment for the entire 1st year must be cleared in full (100%) within 30 days from the date of issue of provisional admission letter, failing which the provisional admission will be cancelled and the refund (as applicable) will be reversed/credited, or pay the late fine as applicable. <br/>
    I/we, the undersigned (candidate and/or Parent/Guardian), accept and declare that I/we have not and/or will not pay any cash/additional fee amount (or any unaccounted money) to anyone for seeking this admission. 
    I/we have/will have no objection and hereby permit the unconditional cancellation of this admission offered, if found involved in any financial transactions related to this admission (beyond the above fee mentioned) within Jan-Dec 2024, by the candidate and/or Parent/Guardian, or on behalf of the candidate/parent.</i>
</div>
